  "texts": [
    "For the fine-tuning step, we plugged a layer for named entity recognition (without Conditional Random Fields) on top of the Spanish BERT.",
    "We implemented it in PyTorch with the Transformers library [69].",
    "We trained for 4 epochs, as in the BERT paper [21].",
    "We make available a Python notebook with the code for the replicability of results.",
    "Experiment methodsThe procedure followed a standard methodology."
  ]
